import React from "react";
import { Col, Row } from "react-bootstrap";
import { CgCPlusPlus } from "react-icons/cg";
import {
  DiPython,
  DiJavascript1,
  DiGit,
  DiJava,
} from "react-icons/di";
import {
  SiMysql,
  SiPostgresql,
  SiMetasploit,
  SiNmap,
  SiWireshark,
  SiBurpsuite,
  SiGhidra,
  SiIdapro,
  SiNessus,
  SiOpenvas
} from "react-icons/si";

function Techstack() {
  return (
    <Row style={{ justifyContent: "center", paddingBottom: "50px" }}>
      {/* Programming Languages */}
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <CgCPlusPlus />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <DiJava />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <DiPython />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <DiJavascript1 />
      </Col>

      {/* Databases */}
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiMysql />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiPostgresql />
      </Col>

      {/* Cybersecurity Tools */}
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiMetasploit />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiNmap />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiWireshark />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiBurpsuite />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiGhidra />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiIdapro />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiNessus />
      </Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <SiOpenvas />
      </Col>

      {/* Version Control */}
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">
        <DiGit />
      </Col>
    </Row>
  );
}

export default Techstack;
